author: LegoBatmanLandon
title: yoda's hut with pink vines
review:
this is a neat set with a neat bike and a awesome hut that looks a lot like Yoda's hut. it includes 3 exclusive figures. this set is good to play with and to display. overall 6/10. neat set. cool pieces. great models.

 

Pros: all the figures are exclusive, there are a lot of cool pieces, the hut is amazing, the bike is neat.

Cons: the birds are all one piece so they can't be customized or taken apart, the tree trunk on the top falls off a lot.
